297
00:28:40,092 --> 00:28:42,804
Oh, baby, it wasn't the right thing.

298
00:28:43,763 --> 00:28:46,098
It's not what the job is.

299
00:28:46,933 --> 00:28:49,519
I'm supposed to be better than that.

300
00:28:50,436 --> 00:28:53,773
And you made one mistake.

301
00:28:55,274 --> 00:28:58,110
No, it wasn't one mistake. I've been...

302
00:29:00,571 --> 00:29:02,532
I've been...

303
