310
00:29:33,855 --> 00:29:36,732
Ever since that Salamanca thing.

311
00:29:37,149 --> 00:29:38,943
I mean, Tuco Salamanca.

312
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:43,072
If ever a scumbag deserved a bullet
between the eyes...

313
00:29:47,827 --> 00:29:49,996
It changed me.

314
00:29:54,500 --> 00:29:57,169
And I can't seem to control it.

315
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:02,925
I tried to fight it.

316
00:30:05,469 --> 00:30:07,138
But then

317
00:30:07,430 --> 00:30:09,098
El Paso.

318
00:30:10,391 --> 00:30:12,894
And it's just gotten worse.

319
00:30:16,355 --> 00:30:18,524
What I did to Pinkman...

320
00:30:21,193 --> 00:30:24,697
that's not who I'm supposed to be.
That's not me.

321
00:30:27,867 --> 00:30:29,702
All this

322
00:30:31,162 --> 00:30:33,539
everything that's happened, I...

323
00:30:34,916 --> 00:30:38,336
I swear to God, Marie,
I think the universe

324
00:30:39,045 --> 00:30:41,213
is trying to tell me something,

325
00:30:41,422 --> 00:30:43,549
and I'm finally

326
00:30:44,675 --> 00:30:46,719
ready to listen.

327
00:30:54,518 --> 00:30:57,730
