328
00:31:01,067 --> 00:31:03,569
I think I'm done as a cop.

329
00:31:14,330 --> 00:31:19,835
Now, this is not an easy decision,
but it is one that I have to make.

330
00:31:20,002 --> 00:31:21,712
I'm sorry.

331
00:31:21,879 --> 00:31:26,759
This whole Gale situation, he's...

332
00:31:26,968 --> 00:31:29,428
He's just not working out.

333
00:31:32,348 --> 00:31:34,392
Yes, now.

334
00:31:34,850 --> 00:31:37,603
It may sound unorthodox,

335
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:43,609
but I think our first best option

336
00:31:45,403 --> 00:31:47,863
is Jesse Pinkman.

337
00:31:51,575 --> 00:31:53,119
Hello?

338
00:31:59,792 --> 00:32:04,964
No, look. There's a shorthand
that exists between us

339
00:32:05,131 --> 00:32:06,924
experience together

340
00:32:07,091 --> 00:32:12,638
at a level that, quite frankly,
I'm just never going to reach with Gale.

341
00:32:17,268 --> 00:32:19,937
Look, Mr. Fring

342
00:32:20,646 --> 00:32:25,985
