I was told the lab is mine.

343
00:32:26,152 --> 00:32:28,654
And I know best how to run it.

344
00:32:33,993 --> 00:32:35,536
Thank you.

345
00:32:36,287 --> 00:32:37,329
Thank you.

346
00:32:37,496 --> 00:32:40,416
Yes, I will. I will.

347
00:32:40,583 --> 00:32:43,044
Okay. Goodbye.

348
00:32:49,967 --> 00:32:51,927
