a monkey?

354
00:33:13,157 --> 00:33:14,950
I don't want a monkey.

355
00:33:15,117 --> 00:33:17,203
I want you.

356
00:33:17,369 --> 00:33:19,705
Oh, gee, thanks.

357
00:33:19,872 --> 00:33:22,208
Well, not interested.

358
00:33:23,042 --> 00:33:26,212
I got my own thing going on.

359
00:33:26,378 --> 00:33:30,466
And nice try, saving your asshead
brother-in-law.

360
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:37,348
