361
00:33:37,515 --> 00:33:39,183
There's more.

362
00:33:40,392 --> 00:33:43,395
It's more than an assistant.

363
00:33:44,105 --> 00:33:45,564
Partners.

364
00:33:47,066 --> 00:33:48,734
We'll be partners again.

365
00:33:48,901 --> 00:33:52,404
Split everything fifty-fifty,
just like before.

366
00:33:54,406 --> 00:33:59,203
One-point-five million dollars each.

367
00:34:05,251 --> 00:34:07,044
No.

368
00:34:12,716 --> 00:34:18,013
- I don't think you heard...
- I heard you fine.

369
00:34:19,223 --> 00:34:21,267
