373
00:34:34,864 --> 00:34:38,242
I am turning down you.

374
00:34:38,409 --> 00:34:40,286
You get it?

375
00:34:40,578 --> 00:34:44,456
I want nothing to do with you.

376
00:34:45,791 --> 00:34:48,377
Ever since I met you

377
00:34:48,586 --> 00:34:52,923
everything I've ever cared about

378
