with the great Heisenberg.

381
00:35:05,686 --> 00:35:08,939
I have never been more alone.

382
00:35:09,607 --> 00:35:12,318
I have nothing!

383
00:35:12,484 --> 00:35:14,570
No one!

384
00:35:15,112 --> 00:35:17,573
All right? It's all gone!

385
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:19,491
Get it?

386
00:35:20,659 --> 00:35:21,785
No.

387
00:35:21,952 --> 00:35:24,580
No, no. Why...?

388
00:35:25,331 --> 00:35:29,001
